                  <div class=\"l-accordion js-acc-wrapper icons-arrows\" data-animation=\"js\" data-scroll-to-view=\"true\" data-start-closed=\"true\">\n                            <div class=\"c-accordion -medium\">\n                                                                                                            <div class=\"c-accordion__item js-acc-item\">\n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"c-accordion__title-wrap -h4\">\n                                                <button class=\"js-acc-button c-accordion__title\">\n                                                    <span class=\"c-accordion__title-count\">\n                                                        01                                                    <\/span>\n                                                    <span>How often should I post on my social media channels?<\/span>\n                                                <\/button>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"js-acc-content\">\n                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__content is-wysiwyg\">\n                                                                                                            <div class=\"text-medium\">\n                                                            <p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Posting too often can be overwhelming for your followers, while posting too little\u00a0can make it difficult to maintain a consistent presence.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559685\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">So, what is the sweet spot?<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559685\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">A <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/sproutsocial.com\/insights\/index\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">recent<\/span><\/a><span data-contrast=\"none\"> industry report found that posting 1-2 times a day can help you stay visible without bombarding your followers with too much information at once.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559685\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">However, your social media presence ultimately depends on your target audience.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">At Digital Silk, we\u2019ll conduct research into your industry, audience and user behavior, and craft a custom social media strategy for your brand.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559685\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>                                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__item js-acc-item\">\n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"c-accordion__title-wrap -h4\">\n                                                <button class=\"js-acc-button c-accordion__title\">\n                                                    <span class=\"c-accordion__title-count\">\n                                                        02                                                    <\/span>\n                                                    <span>Which social media platforms should I utilize?<\/span>\n                                                <\/button>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"js-acc-content\">\n                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__content is-wysiwyg\">\n                                                                                                            <div class=\"text-medium\">\n                                                            <p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Deciding which social media platform to use for your business can be a difficult task \u2013 which is where we come in!<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Ask yourself these questions to help you narrow down the field:<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{\"335552541\":1,\"335559684\":-2,\"335559685\":720,\"335559991\":360,\"469769226\":\"Symbol\",\"469769242\":[8226],\"469777803\":\"left\",\"469777804\":\"\uf0b7\",\"469777815\":\"hybridMultilevel\"}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\"><strong>What demographics are you trying to reach?<\/strong> Different social media platforms have different user bases, so it\u2019s important to select one that aligns with your target audience.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"8\" data-list-defn-props=\"{\"335552541\":1,\"335559684\":-2,\"335559685\":720,\"335559991\":360,\"469769226\":\"Symbol\",\"469769242\":[8226],\"469777803\":\"left\",\"469777804\":\"\uf0b7\",\"469777815\":\"hybridMultilevel\"}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\"><strong>What kind of content are you looking to share?<\/strong> If you\u2019re planning on sharing mostly visual content, then platforms like Instagram and Pinterest may be a good fit. If you\u2019re looking to share mostly written content, then Facebook and Twitter may be better options.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Our social media experts will help you identify which social media platforms are best for your business, based on your target market\u2019s online behavior.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Drop us a note and request a quote!<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>                                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__item js-acc-item\">\n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"c-accordion__title-wrap -h4\">\n                                                <button class=\"js-acc-button c-accordion__title\">\n                                                    <span class=\"c-accordion__title-count\">\n                                                        03                                                    <\/span>\n                                                    <span>How much do social media marketing services cost?<\/span>\n                                                <\/button>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"js-acc-content\">\n                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__content is-wysiwyg\">\n                                                                                                            <div class=\"text-medium\">\n                                                            <p>Organic social media marketing services can cost a minimum of $2,500 to as much as $12,000 or more per month.<\/p>\n<p>The cost of social media marketing services depends on several factors, including your goals, posting frequency and creatives.<\/p>\n<p>Contact our experts to request a free custom quote!<\/p>                                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__item js-acc-item\">\n                                            \n                                            <div class=\"c-accordion__title-wrap -h4\">\n                                                <button class=\"js-acc-button c-accordion__title\">\n                                                    <span class=\"c-accordion__title-count\">\n                                                        04                                                    <\/span>\n                                                    <span>How long will it take until I see significant results from your social media marketing efforts?<\/span>\n                                                <\/button>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                            <div class=\"js-acc-content\">\n                                                <div class=\"c-accordion__content is-wysiwyg\">\n                                                                                                            <div class=\"text-medium\">\n                                                            <p>Your social media results will depend on different factors such as:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Are you investing in organic or paid?<\/li>\n<li>What is the current stage of your social media marketing? Did you just launch your marketing campaigns?<\/li>\n<li>What is the current state of your social media audiences? How big is your following? How engaged are your followers?<\/li>\n<li>What is your current cost-per-lead rate for paid efforts?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>New channels, as well as channels with disengaged audiences, may require more than three months to produce notable results, while existing channels may show results two months after hiring professional services.<\/p>\n<p>Social media marketing requires continuous optimization as algorithms and user behavior evolve.<\/p>\n<p>But don\u2019t worry, as we will keep a close eye on your ads and campaigns and adjust as needed, to ensure you are achieving significant and measurable results.<\/p>\n<p>Get a free estimate of your website project!<\/p>                                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                                                <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"sections-group section-raq bg-dark\">\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"spinner in-view-r\">\n\t<div class=\"spinner-inn\">\n\t\t<img\n                  data-srcset=\"\n                          https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/themes\/digitalsilk\/assets\/_dist\/images\/gradient-bg-sm.png 1440w,\n                          https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/themes\/digitalsilk\/assets\/_dist\/images\/gradient-bg.png 1660w\"\n                  data-src=\"https:\/